European Stocks Gain for Fourth Day in Five; Rio Tinto Leads Mining Rally

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-03-23T16:37:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/european-stocks-gain-for-fourth-day-in-five-rio-tinto-leads-mining-rally.html
European stocks gained for the
fourth time in five days as mining companies climbed with base-
metal prices.  The Stoxx Europe 600 Index advanced 0.4 percent to 272.76
at 4:36 p.m. in  London .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
